snippet.title: PlayStation - Mahou Shoujo Pretty Sammy Part 2 - In the Julyhelm (1997) - Intro
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Mahou Shoujo Pretty Sammy Part 2: In the Julyhelm is an Adventure game, published by Pioneer LDC, which was released in Japan in 1997.
